cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with building detection in aerial images using CNNs and segmentation techniques. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new fusion strategy based on a deep combiner using segmentation results of different CNNs. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques to improve building detection in aerial images. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with processing and analyzing aerial images. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with extracting information from aerial images using CNNs and segmentation techniques.
